These are the installation instructions for Openglad.

INSTALL
=======

1. Unpack the tarball into some directory.
2. Linux: Execute `make` to compile openglad, `make openscen`
   to compile the scenario editor
   Windows: A Visual C++ Makefile can be found in src/. You might need to
   edit the paths to the SDL lib/includes. (Thanks Murlock)
3. openglad is the game binary, openscen is the editor.



If you get Openglad to work on any other operating systems,
please tell us how you did. You can contact one of the
Snowstorm Entertainment guys or post on the forums.
